        <abstract> 
<p>Has quoted WDF on crossing white and slate muscovy ducks [<hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> 2: 40]. When not crossed, do these breed true?</p>  
<p>Will also quote him on Mr Woodd’s white ewes that produced black lambs by a ram with only black spots [<hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> 2: 30].</p> 
